---
title: Firecracker Turkey Meatloaves with Soy-Ginger Glaze & Roasted Zucchini & Broccoli
description: Our iconic firecracker sauce—creamy, spicy, sweet, and savory—elevates tender turkey meatloaves to delicious new heights. The loaves are glazed with an umami-rich soy-ginger sauce and roasted alongside broccoli and zucchini. A final drizzle of firecracker sauce completes the meal.
